name: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Wendy Jane RICKLES.

court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Wendy Jane RICKLES.

opinions.text: Wendy Jane Rickles, of Worcester, Massachusetts, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.

casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Wendy Jane RICKLES.
No. D-2801.
Supreme Court of the United States
Aug. 29, 2014.
Opinion
